@startuml SC-39-Dashboard-Client
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Consulter Dashboard (Client)

object Client
object "Dashboard Client" as Dashboard
object "Service Analytics" as ServiceAnalytics
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit

Client --> Dashboard : 1: acceder("Dashboard")
Dashboard --> ServiceAnalytics : 2: obtenirMetriquesDashboard(clientId)
ServiceAnalytics --> BaseDonnees : 3: executerRequete(statistiques)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceAnalytics : 3.1: donneeMetriques

ServiceAnalytics --> ServiceAudit : 3.2: enregistrerAction("DASHBOARD_CLIENT_CONSULTE")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 3.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceAnalytics --> Dashboard : 4: afficher(metriques)
Dashboard --> Client : 4.1: montrer(dashboard)

note right of ServiceAnalytics
Metriques Client:
- Nombre employes
- Fiches paie recues
- Documents archives
- Alertes importantes
end note

@enduml
